{"type": "article", "id": 5241, "title": "Skull 主题腕表", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-15T07:59:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052335312FZthuGTPAkxdqfN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t瑞士独立制表品牌 HYT 日前发布了一款 Skull 主题腕表。与 HYT 旗下的两款经典腕表 H1 与 H2 一样，Skull 腕表沿用了 HYT 著名的液压动力显示计时系统，设计团队以管道式的轮廓呈现了内部的多彩液体，环绕着表盘中央位置的骷髅状压力泵，Geek 感十足。玫瑰金与黑色 DLC 钛金属表壳搭配红色液体的款式，全球限量发售 25 块，黑色 DLC 钛金属表壳搭配绿色液体款，全球限量发行 50 块，于今年 5 月在指定商铺正式发售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335293PV68gIj9xCaw07K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233529xDZGCt5vW2SsmdpE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523352958L6KPMlaZtu9VXJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.3828125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233530aL1uVmxB4hZTvAQw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1046875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}